entry.content: Stage Fright Sucks! 🥲 Ever since I was 4 I had this irrational fear of dancing in-front of people. I had a Bharatanatyam (If I remember correctly) dance recital at 4 and ran off the stage crying in fear. Never danced again. 😭 My husband didn’t see me dance up until we started doing dancing videos for social media. I’m slowly getting out of my comfort zone but I still feel awkward. My husband and kids have been my biggest support system in tackling my fear. They always hype me up and never judge. 🫶🏽 Love them all! Thanks to all of my followers too! Y’all are awesome! #dance #fyp #fypシ #momof9 #hype #family #supportsystem #parentsof9 #stagefright
